# ðŸ“ˆ Stock Price Prediction using Linear Regression (KNIME)

## Overview
This project predicts future stock prices based on historical market data using a supervised machine learning model built in KNIME Analytics Platform.

## Dataset
- Source: ADANIPORTS__EQ__NSE__MINUTE.csv  
- Features used: DateTime, Open, High, Low, Close, Volume  
- Target: Close Price  

## Steps Performed
1. Imported dataset into KNIME using CSV Reader.  
2. Created lag features using Lag Column node.  
3. Calculated price and volume changes using Math Formula.  
4. Trained Linear Regression model using past prices as inputs.  
5. Evaluated model using Numeric Scorer (RÂ², RMSE, MAE).  

## Model Used
- Algorithm: Linear Regression  
- Type: Supervised Learning  
- Evaluation Metrics: RÂ², RMSE, MAE  

## Results
- RÂ²: ~0.85  
- RMSE: ~12.4    

## Tools Used
- KNIME Analytics Platform  
- CSV Reader, Lag Column, Math Formula, Linear Regression Learner, Numeric Scorer  

